HEADWORD: Upstare
<hw>Up*stare"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To stare or stand
upward; hence, to be uplifted or conspicuous.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Rearing
fiercely their <xex>upstaring</xex> crests.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
